highlights.text: “Dekhya Kite” by Davy, Gur Sidhu, and Simar Kaur is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Jaipur, up 31 spots at #69.
Pritam has the most spots on Top Songs Jaipur. “Kesariya” is the highest at #12.
“Balam Pichkari” by Pritam, Vishal Dadlani, and Shalmali Kholgade is the highest new entry on Top Songs Jaipur at #57.
